---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
import ImageWithFallBack from "./ImageWithFallBack.astro"
---
<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-black to-gray-900 text-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-3 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8 items-center min-h-[500px] md:min-h-[600px] py-12 md:py-16">
          {/* Texto */}
          <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 text-center lg:text-left">
            <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-tight">
              Aqui, seu treino é nossa{" "}
              <span class="text-blue-500">prioridade</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-lg mx-auto lg:mx-0">
              Na Kavera Cross, você encontra o ambiente perfeito para alcançar seus objetivos com equipamentos de última geração e profissionais qualificados.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start">
              <Button size="lg" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 sm:px-8 py-3">
                Comece Agora
              </Button>
              <Button 
                variant="outline" 
                size="lg" 
                class="border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-black px-6 sm:px-8 py-3"
              >
                Conheça os Planos
              </Button>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Imagem */}
          <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end mt-8 lg:mt-0">
            <div class="relative">
              <ImageWithFallBack
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1717500250973-7c345a36a7ac?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=M3w3Nzg4Nzd8MHwxfHNlYXJjaHwxfHx3b21hbiUyMHBob25lJTIwZ3ltJTIwZml0bmVzc3xlbnwxfHx8fDE3NTYxNjIwMzN8MA&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&q=80&w=1080&utm_source=figma&utm_medium=referral"
                alt="Mulher segurando celular na academia"
                class="w-full max-w-xs sm:max-w-sm md:max-w-md lg:max-w-lg rounded-lg shadow-2xl grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300"
              />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-600 opacity-20 rounded-lg"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>